videos.description: During a dead ball, players from Iowa and Illinois jaw at each other, with Iowa's Connor McCaffery and Illinois' Da'Monte Williams each receiving technical fouls.
videos.headline: Tempers flare between Iowa, Illinois

videos.description: Ayo Dosunmu dishes to Trent Frazier, who knocks down the corner 3-pointer to cap an 8-0 Illinois run and force an Iowa timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Illinois bench goes wild over Frazier's 3) 2020/03/08

videos.headline: Illinois bench goes wild over Frazier's 3

videos.description: Illinois' Ayo Dosunmu gets the ball in transition and breaks out a Eurostep to get by Luka Garza for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dosunmu Eurosteps past Garza for Illinois bucket) 2020/03/08

videos.headline: Dosunmu Eurosteps past Garza for Illinois bucket

videos.description: Iowa's Luka Garza gets the ball in the post and spins around an Illinois defender to create space and get the easy bucket down low.
videos.headline: Garza spins baseline to score

videos.description: Trailing by two in the final seconds, Iowa's Luka Garza hoists up a game-tying attempt, but Kofi Cockburn swats the shot away to seal Illinois' win.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Garza blocked at the buzzer, Illinois hangs on for win) 2020/03/08

videos.headline: Garza blocked at the buzzer, Illinois hangs on for win
